bag containing six halfbaked loaves of bread shouts 1000 
pounds who pays higher 
1200 said a hungry resident of the christian enclave 
lunging at the bag 
the 250 price tag five times the regular amount enrages the 
other four men bidding for the scarce commodity and they chase the 
auctioneer away with shouts of thief thief 
shelves in the few grocery stories that were open in the furn 
elshubbak and neighboring ein rummaneh residential areas hardhit 
by fighting between rival christian forces were nearly empty 
friday 
hunger drove some residents to brave the sniper fire at the 
