the profession who would stop by the downtown location 
before voting to close the pen amp pencil club officials even 
considered holding aerobics classes and childcare groups moves 
the older reporters dismissed 
the pen amp pencil was losing 300 to 400 a week when the clubs 
officers voted last month to close down 
