chancellor helmut kohl of west germany arrived in 
moscow today for talks aimed at reassuring the soviets that a 
reunited germany would not threaten their security 
kohl accompanied by foreign minister hansdietrich genscher 
was to meet with president mikhail s gorbachev in one of a series 
