to john odonnell the allegations of sexual 
misconduct against the rev bruce ritter are beside the point the 
point he says is that covenant house gives him a clean place to 
sleep each night 
he feeds us he clothes us and were behind him 100 percent 
said odonnell 20 who found shelter at covenant house two weeks 
