the day before ritter had stepped down as executive director of 
covenant house pending an investigation by the franciscans the 
order of roman catholic priests to which ritter belongs of charges 
that he had had sexual relations with several youths who had sought 
his help 
ritter dismisses the allegations as garbage and odonnell 
and many of his fellow covenant house residents agree even those 
who think ritters accusers could be telling the truth say it 
doesnt diminish their gratitude for a man whose work changed their 
