advertising director in 1953 and in 1969 was named a vice 
president of the company which publishes the greenville news and 
greenville piedmont 
born in elgin tuesdale was a former resident of columbia where 
he was associated with the state newspaper 
he is survived by a daughter and soninlaw two grandchildren 
and one greatgrandchild 
